Package: bitmusic
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: SyberianIT <info@syberianit.com>
Installed-Size: 50000
Depends: libgtk-3-0 (>= 3.24), liblzma5, libglib2.0-0, libgstreamer1.0-0, libgstreamer-plugins-base1.0-0, gstreamer1.0-plugins-good, gstreamer1.0-plugins-bad, ffmpeg
Recommends: gstreamer1.0-libav
Section: sound
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/syberianit/bitmusic
Description: BitMusic — Music Search & Download
 Search YouTube for any track by name, artist or lyrics.
 Download audio in high quality (AAC/OPUS, auto-converted to MP3 192 kbps
 when ffmpeg is available).
 Play downloaded tracks offline with the built-in player.
 .
 Supported platforms: Linux, Android, iOS, Windows.
